---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const updated = 'April 24, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — ParentCompass"
  description="Terms governing your use of ParentCompass and our waitlist service."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-sand-50 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">

      <p class="text-terra-500 text-xs font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm font-sans mb-12">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <div class="prose-legal">

        <h2>1. Acceptance of terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing parentcompass.ai or joining our waitlist, you agree to these Terms of
          Service. If you do not agree, please do not use our site or submit your email address.
        </p>

        <h2>2. What ParentCompass is</h2>
        <p>
          ParentCompass is a pre-launch AI-powered college counselling service. At this time, the
          product is not available. The website exists to collect interest from families ahead of
          our launch. No paid subscription, account, or service is offered through this website
          at present.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Waitlist</h2>
        <p>
          By joining the waitlist, you are expressing interest in ParentCompass and consenting to
          receive email updates about our launch and pricing. Joining the waitlist does not
          guarantee access to the product, create a contract, or obligate ParentCompass to launch
          by any particular date.
        </p>
        <p>
          You may remove yourself from the waitlist at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link
          in any email we send, or by contacting us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@parentcompass.ai">hello@parentcompass.ai</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>
          All content on parentcompass.ai — including text, graphics, logos, and design — is
          owned by or licensed to ParentCompass. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create
          derivative works from our content without written permission.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
        <p>
          This website is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. ParentCompass makes no
          representations about the accuracy or completeness of any content on this site.
          Information about the planned product (features, pricing, launch date) is subject to
          change without notice.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, ParentCompass shall not be liable for any
          indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of this website
          or your participation in the waitlist.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Links to third-party sites</h2>
        <p>
          Our site may contain links to third-party websites. These links are provided for
          convenience only. We have no control over the content of those sites and accept no
          responsibility for them.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Changes to these terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these terms as the product evolves. We will notify waitlist members by
          email of any material changes. Your continued use of the site after changes constitutes
          acceptance of the updated terms.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Governing law</h2>
        <p>
          These terms are governed by the laws of the State of California, United States, without
          regard to conflict of law principles.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these terms? Email us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@parentcompass.ai">hello@parentcompass.ai</a>.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-legal h2 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1A3A2A;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .prose-legal p {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #6B5F4E;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-legal ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-legal li {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #6B5F4E;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    color: #C4603A;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .prose-legal strong {
    color: #4A3F32;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
